TITLE: Create React Email Template - JSX
DESCRIPTION: Creates a basic React Email template using JSX syntax. It imports components from @react-email/components and React, defining a functional component MyEmail which returns an HTML button linking to example.com. Located in packages/transactional/emails/MyEmail.tsx
SOURCE: https://github.com/resend/react-email/blob/canary/apps/docs/getting-started/monorepo-setup/npm.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { Button, Html } from "@react-email/components";
import * as React from "react";

export const MyEmail = () => {
  return (
    <Html>
      <Button
        href="https://example.com"
        style={{ background: "#000", color: "#fff", padding: "12px 20px" }}
      >
        Click me
      </Button>
    </Html>
  );
}

export default MyEmail;
```

